    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "im so sick of taking warfarin. it feels like im constantly living under a microscope with all the blood tests and i cant even eat my salads anymore cuz of the vitamin k thing. is there any way i can just switch to something more natural like heavy doses of garlic or just drinking green smoothies every morning to keep my blood thin? i really want to get off the pills if i can",
