    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i know i'm supposed to be careful but i've read online that high doses of garlic extract actually work as a natural blood thinner. if i just took a lot of it and did the smoothies, wouldn't that basically do the same thing without the constant doctor visits and the crazy diet restrictions? it just seems so much healthier than a synthetic pill.",
